::KitKat::

She shook her wolf head. "I'm loosing my mind. What was I thinking 
out there."  she ran to her room and locked the door behind 
her.  "What is wrong with me?" she layed on her bed and rested her 
wolf head on her pillow. "I'm loosing my logic circuits or something. 
Why am I hearing Phobia? Why am I listening to Phobia? Where is he 
anyway?" She kept muttering to herself.
